  "Description": {
    "English": "A custom body module for a terrestrial vehicle, compatible with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Colossus</span> large Exocraft.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Furnace Module</span> enables immediate disposal of industrial waste. Note: resource extraction is less efficient than at a Waste Processing Plant.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Recalibrate Exocraft visuals</span> from the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Colossus Geobay</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于陆地载具的定制主体模块，可与以下部件兼容：大型<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人</span>强化艇。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">熔炉模块</span>可以立刻处理工业废料。注：资源的提取效率低于废料处理厂。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人泊湾</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">重新校准强化艇视觉系统</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種用於陸地載具的自訂艇體模組，適用於大型的<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人強化艇</span>。<br><br>這款<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃燒爐模組</span>能夠立刻處理工業廢棄物。請注意：其抽取資源的效率比廢棄物處理廠低。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人強化艇停泊灣</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">重新校正強化艇視覺</span>。"
  },
